%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump's%20world%20of%20tariffs%20is%20shaking%20up%20time-tested%20investing%20strategies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wall%20Street%20investing%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677c38d159d276c1cdb045e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELeonardo%20Munoz%2FVIEWpress%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EStocks%20and%20bonds%20both%20fell%20after%20White%20House%20tariffs%20spooked%20investors%20in%20April.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%2060%2F40%20portfolio%20strategy%20is%20one%20of%20several%20conventional%20investing%20approaches%20that's%20struggled.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETariff%20uncertainty%20has%20also%20thrown%20dip%20buying%20and%20US%20stock%20outperformance%20for%20a%20loop.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22%23f2a6f4%5C%22%3EAs%20stocks%20started%20to%20fall%20in%20February%2C%20little%20did%20investors%20know%20that%20some%20of%20their%20most%20tried%20and%20trusted%20strategies%20would%20be%20upended.%3C%2Fmark%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22%23f2a6f4%5C%22%3EInitially%2C%20%3C%2Fmark%3Edisciples%20of%20the%20classic%20portfolio%20allocation%20strategy%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-diversification%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E60%25%20stocks%20and%2040%25%20bonds%3C%2Fa%3E%20breathed%20a%20sigh%20of%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20was%20undergoing%20a%20correction%2C%20bonds%20were%20seeing%20gains%20for%20their%20safe-haven%20appeal.%20Thanks%20to%20recession%20fears%2C%20yields%20on%20risk-free%2010-year%20Treasury%20notes%20had%20fallen%20from%204.8%25%20to%20under%204%25%20(bond%20yields%20are%20inversely%20related%20to%20prices)%20between%20mid-January%20and%20early%20April.%20Diversification%20was%20working%20as%20promised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20after%20the%20White%20House's%20April%202%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20announcement%2C%20things%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStocks%20plummeted%20even%20further.%20But%20Trump's%20proposals%20also%20began%20to%20spook%20bond%20investors%2C%20who%20started%20selling%20off%20their%20holdings%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20rise%20in%20yields.%20The%20move%20motivated%20Trump%20to%20pause%20his%20excess%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%26quot%3B%20tariff%20plans%20for%20most%20countries%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20bond%20market%20is%20very%20tricky%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20on%20April%209.%20%26quot%3BI%20saw%20last%20night%20where%20people%20were%20getting%20a%20little%20queasy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20yields%20have%20risen%20as%20high%20as%204.49%25%20while%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20dropped%20as%20much%20as%2012%25.%20Both%20components%20of%20the%2060%2F40%20are%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20potentially%20a%20few%20reasons%20why%20yields%20started%20rising%2C%20making%20the%2060%2F40%20hedge%20ineffective%20for%20the%20time%20being.%20One%20may%20be%20that%20foreign%20investors%20are%20losing%20confidence%20in%20the%20US%2C%20according%20to%20John%20Pease%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20asset%20allocation%20team%20at%20asset%20management%20firm%20GMO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20it%20seems%20like%20is%20foreigners%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20reassessing%20how%20much%20US%20exposure%20they%20want%20to%20have%20and%20reallocating%20some%20of%20that%20money%20to%20foreign%20assets%2C%26quot%3B%20Pease%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20reason%20we've%20seen%20kind%20of%20these%20concerted%20moves%20in%20US%20equities%2C%20US%20bonds%2C%20and%20the%20US%20dollar%20all%20selling%20off%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20is%20that%20a%20hedge%20fund%20had%20a%20leveraged%20strategy%20known%20as%20a%20basis%20trade%20blow%20up%2C%20causing%20it%20to%20sell-off%20its%20Treasurys%2C%20said%20Lance%20Roberts%2C%20the%20chief%20strategist%20at%20RIA%20Advisors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20inflation%20fears%20are%20also%20part%20of%20the%20mix%2C%20wrote%20Lawrence%20Gillum%2C%20chief%20fixed%20income%20strategist%20at%20LPL%20Financial%2C%20in%20a%20recent%20client%20note.%20Tariffs%20are%20likely%20to%20raise%20prices%2C%20leading%20investors%20to%20demand%20higher%20yields%20to%20compensate%20for%20the%20declining%20value%20of%20money%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20reality%20puts%20a%20wrench%20in%20the%2060%2F40%20going%20forward%2C%20said%20Lauren%20Goodwin%2C%20economist%20and%20chief%20market%20strategist%20at%20New%20York%20Life%20Investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%2060%2F40%20portfolio%20was%20designed%20for%20periods%20of%20low%20inflation%2C%26quot%3B%20Goodwin%20said%20in%20a%20client%20note%20on%20Tuesday.%20%26quot%3BIt%20won't%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20how%20long%20the%2060%2F40%20will%20remain%20ineffective.%20For%20long-term%20investors%2C%20the%20strategy%20is%20still%20viable%2C%20Roberts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%2060%2F40%20allocation%20has%20outperformed%20being%20fully%20invested%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20hands%20down%20over%20the%20last%20130%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20investors%20with%20a%20shorter%20time%20horizon%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20time%20to%20reconsider%20how%20their%20portfolios%20are%20positioned%2C%20said%20Eric%20Markowitz%2C%20managing%20partner%20at%20Nightview%20Capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there's%20a%20strong%20argument%20that%20inflation%20can%20erode%20bond%20returns%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20if%20you're%20getting%20like%20a%203%25%20or%204%25%20yield%20on%20a%20bond%20return%2C%20but%20we%20have%20really%20high%20inflation%2C%20then%20you%20have%20to%20find%20your%20growth%20somewhere%20else.%20So%20it%20definitely%20could%20destabilize%20that%2060%2F40%20dynamic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2227e5549c-ba13-4e42-9e4b-bbb597444dd7%5C%22%3EIt's%20not%20just%20the%2060%2F40%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20conventional%20investing%20strategies%20may%20be%20gone%20for%20now%20as%20well%20%E2%80%94%20one%20being%20that%20the%20US%20is%20the%20best%20place%20to%20find%20returns%2C%20according%20to%20Pease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20particular%20case%20of%20tariffs%20and%20the%20particular%20case%20of%20rather%20erratic%20economic%20policymaking%2C%20there%20is%20every%20reason%20for%20both%20foreign%20and%20domestic%20investors%20to%20say%20they%20are%20less%20comfortable%20holding%20US%20assets%20than%20they've%20been%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Pease%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20is%20true%20of%20equities%2C%20that%20is%20also%20true%20of%20bonds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20European%20and%20Japanese%20bonds%20have%20not%20sold%20off%20as%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20notion%20that%20the%20Fed%20can%20step%20in%20with%20rate%20cuts%20if%20the%20economy%20slows%20is%20also%20not%20a%20given%20in%20today's%20world%20of%20tariffs.%20With%20the%20import%20taxes%20threatening%20to%20boost%20consumer%20prices%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20is%20reluctant%20to%20provide%20more%20juice%20to%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFed%20Chair%20Jerome%20Powell%20acknowledged%20the%20conundrum%20in%20a%20speech%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20obligation%20is%20to%20keep%20longer-term%20inflation%20expectations%20well%20anchored%20and%20to%20make%20certain%20that%20a%20one-time%20increase%20in%20the%20price%20level%20does%20not%20become%20an%20ongoing%20inflation%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20may%20find%20ourselves%20in%20the%20challenging%20scenario%20in%20which%20our%20dual-mandate%20goals%20are%20in%20tension.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2299105a08-89fd-4d90-b80c-e703655b26c9%5C%22%3EWhat's%20an%20investor%20to%20do%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoodwin%20said%20inflation-sensitive%20assets%20are%20good%20bets%20in%20this%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20like%20gold%2C%20broad%20industrial%20metals%2C%20and%20real%20assets%20as%20an%20inflation-aware%20satellite%20to%20a%20portfolio%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Pease%2C%20Japanese%20small-cap%20value%20stocks%20appear%20particularly%20attractive%20at%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarkowitz%20said%20investors%20should%20focus%20on%20high-quality%20stocks%2C%20which%20have%20strong%20track%20records%20of%20earnings%20growth%2C%20low%20debt%20levels%2C%20and%20high%20pricing%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20investors%20shouldn't%20feel%20forced%20to%20make%20changes%20to%20their%20strategy%2C%20Markowitz%20added%2C%20especially%20since%20the%20market%20outlook%20seems%20to%20change%20on%20a%20dime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20certain%20segment%20of%20the%20investing%20public%20that%20feels%20like%20they%20have%20to%20do%20something%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20advocating%20people%20necessarily%20do%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BBy%20tomorrow%2C%20we%20might%20be%20having%20a%20totally%20different%20conversation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-stock-market-investing-strategies-60-40-portfolio-inflation-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745197261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68011d17c6ad288d147e6f4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-stock-market-investing-strategies-60-40-portfolio-inflation-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%2060%2F40%20portfolio%20was%20designed%20for%20periods%20of%20low%20inflation%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20economist%20Lauren%2