about%20eight%20different%20units%2C%20she%20decided%20on%20a%20three-bedroom%20apartment%20in%20Tanjung%20Tokong%2C%20a%20neighborhood%20near%20Penang's%20capital%20city%2C%20George%20Town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%201%2C200%20square%20feet%2C%20with%20a%20small%20balcony%20and%20two%20extra%20bedrooms%20for%20her%20daughters%20or%20friends%20to%20stay%20in%20when%20they%20visit.%20Rent%20is%202%2C000%20Malaysian%20Ringgit%2C%20or%20about%20%24450%2C%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20got%20the%20sea%20view%20she%20wanted%2C%20and%20the%20nearest%20grocery%20store%20is%20five%20minutes%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223ebf206c-d065-44b4-b8c8-a799c3129d71%5C%22%3EA%20slower%20life%2C%20but%20with%20'plenty'%20to%20do%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETozer%20is%20on%20the%20Malaysia%20My%20Second%20Home%2C%20or%20MM2H%2C%20visa%2C%20which%20was%20introduced%20in%202002%20to%20attract%20foreigners%20who%20want%20to%20retire%20and%20live%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%2058%2C468%20active%20MM2H%20pass%20holders%20in%20the%20country%20as%20of%20December%2C%20Malaysia's%20minister%20of%20tourism%2C%20arts%2C%20and%20culture%2C%20Tiong%20King%20Sing%2C%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.parlimen.gov.my%2Ffiles%2Fjindex%2Fpdf%2FJDR24022025.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparliamentary%20response%20on%20February%2024%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bedroom.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f87be8c6ad288d147ddfff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt's%20a%20three-bedroom%20apartment%20with%20plenty%20of%20space%20for%20her%20to%20practice%20yoga.%3Cp%3EJill%20Tozer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Tozer%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20perks%20of%20living%20in%20Malaysia%20has%20been%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-hottest-year-ever-history-climate-crisis-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclimate%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20reason%20I'm%20here%20is%20for%20the%20weather.%20I%20love%20never%20being%20cold%2C%26quot%3B%20Tozer%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20being%20able%20to%20leave%20my%20doors%20and%20windows%20open%20day%20and%20night.%20I%20love%20being%20able%20to%20go%20swimming%20anytime%20I%20want.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20says%20the%20community%20has%20been%20inclusive%20and%20welcoming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20New%20Zealand%2C%20as%20in%20many%20Western%20countries%2C%20older%20people%20are%20kind%20of%20almost%20invisible%2C%20but%20here%20you%20get%20more%20respect.%20People%20are%20actually%20nice%20to%20you%2C%20notice%20you%2C%20and%20want%20to%20help%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Tozer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20view%20from%20her%20balcony.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f87beac6ad288d147de002%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20apartment%20even%20comes%20with%20sea%20views%2C%20exactly%20what%20she%20wanted.%3Cp%3EJill%20Tozer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lower%20cost%20of%20living%20helps%2C%20Tozer%20said.%20Her%20monthly%20living%20expenses%2C%20including%20bills%20and%20food%2C%20are%20often%20less%20than%204%2C000%20Malaysian%20ringgit.%20This%20doesn't%20include%20extras%2C%20like%20travel%20expenses%20if%20she%20decides%20to%20take%20a%20trip%20somewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFood%20for%20me%20is%20very%20cheap.%20I%20don't%20eat%20meat%2C%20dairy%2C%20cheese%2C%20or%20anything%20like%20that%20that's%20imported%20and%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20Tozer%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20eats%20out%20three%20or%20four%20times%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f87be9c6ad288d147de001%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20lower%20cost%20of%20living%20means%20she%20can%20afford%20to%20eat%20out%20more%20often.%3Cp%3EJill%20Tozer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20life%20here%20is%20also%20much%20slower%20than%20it%20used%20to%20be%2C%20partially%20because%20she%20is%20fully%20retired.%20However%2C%20she%20says%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bplenty%26quot%3B%20of%20things%20to%20do%20that%20keep%20her%20busy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYoga%2C%20swimming.%20Play%20Mahjong.%20Play%20Bridge.%20There's%20so%20much%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20so%20nice%20to%20be%20able%20to%20meet%20up%20with%20people%20without%20having%20to%20worry%20about%2C%20'Oh%20my%20God%2C%20how%20much%20is%20this%20going%20to%20cost%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20she%20didn't%20know%20anyone%20in%20Penang%20when%20she%20first%20arrived%2C%20it%20wasn't%20hard%20to%20find%20her%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20joined%20expat%20Facebook%20groups%20and%20began%20attending%20meetups%20hosted%20by%20fellow%20members.%20She's%20still%20friends%20with%20some%20of%20the%20people%20she%20met%20at%20her%20very%20first%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2a03360-1654-477b-a551-245f04df60ff%5C%22%3EDeciding%20what's%20next%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20MM2H%20has%20made%20Malaysia%20an%20attractive%20place%20for%20expats%2C%20the%20most%20recent%20rule%20changes%2C%20announced%20in%202024%2C%20included%20stricter%20financial%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20now%20three%20different%20categories%20of%20the%20visa.%20Depending%20on%20the%20category%20of%20visa%20they%20apply%20for%2C%20applicants%20are%20required%20to%20have%20fixed%20deposits%20of%20between%20%24150%2C000%20and%20%241%20million%20and%20also%20buy%20property%20in%20Malaysia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETozer%20isn't%20due%20to%20renew%20her%20visa%20for%20a%20few%20more%20years%2C%20but%20says%20that%20will%20be%20when%20she%20starts%20thinking%20about%20whether%20she%20wants%20to%20return%20to%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20older%20woman%20with%20her%20daughter%20and%20her%20daughter's%20partner.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f87be8a466d2b74ab2e268%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETozer%20says%20moving%20abroad%20alone%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20as%20scary%26quot%3B%20as%20one%20might%20think.%20In%20this%20photo%2C%20she%20is%20pictured%20with%20one%20of%20her%20daughters%20and%20her%20son-in-law.%3Cp%3EJill%20Tozer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20sure%20at%20this%20point.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20might%20need%20my%20kids%20around%20closer.%20It%20just%20depends%20on%20what%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20Tozer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20her%20time%20in%20Malaysia%20has%20been%20fulfilling%2C%20and%20moving%20to%20a%20new%20country%20alone%20is%20not%20as%20scary%20as%20one%20might%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20reasons%20I%20came%20here%2C%20particularly%20to%20Malaysia%2C%20is%20because%20it's%20safe.%20For%20a%20single%20woman%2C%20that's%20quite%20a%20big%20consideration%2C%26quot%3B%20Tozer%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20lots%20of%20places%20I%20wouldn't%20move%20to%20on%20my%20own%2C%20but%20Malaysia%2C%20no%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20relocating%20to%20a%20new%20city%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aagoh%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eagoh%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-zealander-retired-malaysia-low-