he%20running%20the%20numbers%20and%20getting%20different%20results%20than%20you%3F%20Is%20he%20just%20used%20to%20things%20always%20working%20out%3F%20Or%2C%20is%20he%20simply%20hiding%20the%20enormity%20of%20his%20worry%2C%20but%20is%20actually%20paralyzed%20by%20it%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFiguring%20out%20why%20is%20the%20key%20to%20communicating%20the%20urgency%20of%20the%20problem%20to%20your%20spouse.%20I%20have%20one%20recommendation%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20the%20answer%20is%3A%20Talk%20to%20the%20family%20member%20who%20pays%20your%20mortgage%2C%20and%20ask%20them%20to%20talk%20to%20him%20about%20their%20gift.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20someone%20has%20been%20giving%20you%20something%20for%20long%20enough%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20take%20their%20generosity%20for%20granted%20and%20begin%20seeing%20their%20gift%20as%20another%20form%20of%20income%20rather%20than%20as%20the%20temporary%20reprieve%20that%20it%20is.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhatever%20the%20reasons%20for%20their%20ongoing%20gift%2C%20it's%20important%20that%20they%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20you%20(someone%20he%20may%20already%20view%20as%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20Chicken%20Little)%2C%20remind%20him%20that%20their%20situation%20could%20change%20at%20any%20time%2C%20affecting%20yours%20by%20default.%20Even%20putting%20a%20face%20back%20on%20the%20recurring%20check%20may%20shake%20him%20out%20of%20his%20stupor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20said%2C%20if%20he's%20simply%20working%20with%20a%20different%20set%20of%20calculations%20than%20you%2C%20bringing%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fhow-to-find-financial-advisor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efinancial%20advisor%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20could%20be%20another%20impactful%20way%20to%20demonstrate%20the%20dire%20reality%20of%20your%20situation.%20This%20option%20will%20cost%20money%20that%20I%20know%20you're%20short%20on%2C%20but%20if%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20is%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20get%20your%20spouse%20to%20sell%20thousands%20of%20dollars'%20worth%20of%20assets%20to%20keep%20the%20lights%20on%2C%20it%20will%20be%20worth%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20way%20you%20can%20show%20him%20the%20severity%20of%20your%20financial%20problems%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20he%20sees%20and%20comprehends%20the%20interest%20statements%20on%20your%20credit%20cards%20and%20any%20collection%20letters%20you%20might%20be%20receiving.%20He%20doesn't%20get%20to%20nap%20below%20deck%20while%20you%20try%20to%20outsail%20the%20storm%20alone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20way%20to%20ensure%20this%20is%20to%20put%20him%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20bills.%20As%20you%20already%20know%2C%20being%20the%20one%20to%20move%20debt%20around%20to%20get%20the%20most%20important%20bills%20paid%20on%20time%20and%20spending%20half%20the%20month%20sweating%20over%20which%20will%20hit%20your%20account%20first%20%E2%80%94%20the%20withdrawal%20or%20the%20deposit%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20highly%20stressful%20way%20to%20live.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20flip%20side%20of%20this%2C%20avoiding%20these%20realities%20affords%20you%20a%20level%20of%20blissful%20ignorance%20that%20tends%20to%20breed%20irresponsible%20financial%20habits.%20So%2C%20let%20him%20learn%20the%20hard%20way.%20If%20he%20is%20a%20reasonable%2C%20intelligent%20person%2C%20he%20won't%20shrug%20off%20%2425%2C000%20in%20credit%20card%20debt.%20When%20he%20feels%20that%20this%20number%20is%20his%20problem%20to%20solve%2C%20he%20will%20have%20little%20other%20choice%20than%20to%20look%20at%20his%20big-ticket%20possessions%20very%20differently.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere's%20also%20always%20the%20last%20possibility%20I%20posited.%20Your%20spouse%20may%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20problem%20and%20feel%20paralyzed%20by%20anxiety.%20If%20this%20is%20the%20case%2C%20there's%20nothing%20to%20be%20gained%20by%20hitting%20him%20over%20the%20head%20with%20the%20enormity%20of%20the%20problem.%20Instead%2C%20try%20breaking%20the%20problem%20down%20into%20doable%20chunks.%20You%20may%20want%20to%20consult%20with%20a%20financial%20planner%20for%20this%20as%20well%2C%20or%20you%20could%20look%20into%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score%2Fwhat-is-debt-relief%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edebt%20relief%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20programs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHonestly%2C%20in%20the%20face%20of%20disaster%2C%20I%20tend%20to%20freeze%20rather%20than%20fight.%20So%2C%20I%20know%20firsthand%20that%20stopping%20the%20bleeding%20and%20having%20a%20straightforward%20treatment%20plan%20is%20about%20the%20only%20way%20to%20get%20me%20unstuck%20and%20back%20in%20action.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20all%20your%20spouse%20knows%20is%20that%20the%20already%20massive%20problem%20is%20growing%20by%20the%20minute%2C%20being%20told%20to%20sell%20his%20prized%20possessions%20or%20to%20vaguely%20%26quot%3Bmake%20more%20cash%26quot%3B%20may%20seem%20as%20pointless%20as%20it%20is%20hopeless.%20This%20doesn't%20mean%20you%20should%20minimize%20the%20issue%20to%20keep%20him%20comfortable.%20Instead%2C%20offer%20him%20a%20clear%20plan%20for%20solving%20the%20issue.%20This%20won't%20just%20show%20him%20the%20tangible%20value%20of%20selling%20his%20big-ticket%20items%3B%20he%20may%20also%20feel%20capable%20of%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20family%20crises%2C%20being%20the%20only%20person%20who%20seems%20to%20recognize%20the%20issue%20and%20the%20only%20one%20interested%20in%20solving%20it%20can%20feel%20overwhelming%20%E2%80%94%20in%20other%20words%2C%20you%20might%20feel%20the%20same%20way%20your%20spouse%20feels.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERemember