%20height%3D%5C%222349%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20TAP%20Air%20flight%20vouchers%20I%20was%20given%20when%20our%20flight%20was%20overbooked.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20around%201%20a.m.%20by%20the%20time%20we%20got%20to%20our%20Madeira%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2279f2a8d7-35d4-4073-bb03-28810c472fb8%5C%22%3ESoon%2C%20we%20were%20surprised%20with%20another%20flight%20cancellation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20looking%20at%20a%20sunrise%20in%20Madeira.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f57e1c3fe8d39283627c80%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20changed%20plans%20and%20watched%20a%20sunrise%20over%20Pico%20Areeiro%20in%20Madeira%20to%20fit%20another%20activity%20in.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20around%204%20p.m.%2C%20we%20got%20an%20email%20notifying%20us%20that%20our%20return%20flight%20to%20Lisbon%20in%20two%20days%20was%20canceled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20hours%20after%20receiving%20that%20message%2C%20we%20were%20notified%20that%20we%20had%20been%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eautomatically%20booked%20for%20a%20new%2C%209%20p.m.%20flight%20on%20the%20day%20we%20planned%20to%20leave%20%E2%80%94%20a%20full%2012%20hours%20later%20than%20our%20original%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrustrated%2C%20my%20friend%20booked%20us%20on%20an%20earlier%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fryanair-flight-review-first-time-bag-fees-charges-wasnt-convinced-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERyanair%20flight%3C%2Fa%3E%20back%20to%20Lisbon%20instead%2C%20which%20cost%20%24113%20each.%20Once%20again%2C%20we%20changed%20plans%20and%20unexpectedly%20spent%20more%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20going%20to%20Sintra%2C%20as%20we%20planned%20the%20first%20time%20our%20fli