%22%3E%3Cem%3Ea%20married%20couple%20living%20in%20Charleston%2C%20South%20Carolina%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20The%20two%20have%20residential-renovation%20experience%2C%20but%20bought%20their%20first%20commercial%20property%2C%20a%20laundromat%2C%20in%202022.%20The%20conversations%20have%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EErin%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt%20was%20definitely%20Jon's%20idea%20to%20buy%20a%20laundromat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20down%20a%20rabbit%20hole%20on%20YouTube%20with%20laundromats%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20is%20an%20entrepreneur%2C%20he%20went%20to%20business%20school%20%E2%80%94%20so%20he'd%20always%20heard%20that%20they%20were%20a%20good%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20we%20were%20thinking%20%E2%80%94%20well%2C%20he%20was%20thinking%20%E2%80%94%20why%20not%20try%20a%20laundromat%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJon%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20had%20a%20marketing%20business%20that%20I%20saved%20some%20money%20from%2C%20and%20I%20was%20just%20seeing%20it%20deflate.%20I%20think%20the%20inflation%20had%20started%2C%20and%20we%20started%20seeing%20high%20inflation%20numbers%20at%208%25%2C%209%25%2C%20and%2010%25.%20And%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20a%20good%20recessionary%20business%20that%20does%20well%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20a%20background%20in%20traveling%20and%20going%20to%20laundromats%2C%20and%20then%20this%20one%20came.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EErin%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20was%20very%2C%20very%20cheap.%20And%20we%20went%20to%20see%20it%2C%20and%20we%20saw%20why%20it%20was%20very%2C%20very%20cheap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221179%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20laundromat%20before%20a%20renovation.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68015141c6ad288d147e7b9a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20laundromat%20before%20the%20renovation.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Erin%20Carpenter.%3C%2