This%20story%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20heard%20about%20the%20Pacific%20Crest%20Trail%20when%20I%20was%2018%2C%20and%20because%20I'm%20from%20Washington%20and%20grew%20up%20in%20Seattle%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20walking%20home%20really%20appealed%20to%20me.%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20it%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20consultant%20at%20PricewaterhouseCoopers%20and%20decided%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20a%20program%20they%20have%20where%20you%20can%20take%20paid%20leave%20and%20receive%2020%25%20of%20your%20pay.%20In%20my%20mind%2C%20doing%20a%20thru-hike%20would%20be%20a%20one-and-done.%20You%20do%20that%20once%20in%20your%20life%20and%20move%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hike%20took%20me%20five%20months.%20When%20I%20finished%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I'd%20just%20done%20this%20really%20amazing%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20I%20went%20back%20to%20work.%20It%20was%20a%20really%20hard%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20team%20had%20also%20changed%20while%20I%20was%20gone.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20didn't%20even%20know%20what%20kind%20of%20work%20I%20was%20doing%20anymore.%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20my%20future%20at%20the%20company%20looked%20like%2C%20even%20though%20I%20loved%20the%20work%20I%20was%20doing%20before%20I%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20quit%20my%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20last%20day%20of%20work%20was%20Wednesday%2C%20and%20I'm%20starting%20my%20next%20thru-hike%20on%20Monday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20doing%20the%20Continental%20Divide%20Trail%20and%20linking%20it%20up%20with%20the%20Great%20Divide%20Trail%20in%20Canada.%20The%20route%20follows%20the%20mountain%20ranges%20that%20divide%20the%20continent%2C%20from%20New%20Mexico%20to%20Kakwa%20Lakes%20in%20British%20Columbia.%20The%20total%20mileage%20is%203%2C700%20and%20I'm%20hoping%20to%20finish%20in%20about%20five%20months.%20I'm%20planning%20to%20average%20over%2030%20miles%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20able%20to%20walk%20into%20another%20country%20and%20continue%20onward%20on%20the%20same%20trail%20for%20another%20700%20miles%20just%20seemed%20like%20a%20really%20unique%20way%20to%20experience%20this%20part%20of%20the%20country%2C%20which%20is%20so%20beautiful%20and%20wild.%20I%20want%20to%20do%20things%20that%20scare%20me%2C%20and%20this%20route%20scares%20me.%20It's%20also%20my%2030th%20birthday%20this%20year%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20send%20myself%20off%20with%20a%20big%20bang.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jessica%20Guo%20outdoors%20hiking%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6802a6dea466d2b74ab39ead%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJessica%20Guo%20hiked%20the%20PCT%20in%202023.%3Cp%3EJessica%20Guo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e8fd8778-cd50-4fbf-a906-472df4d721c7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHiking%20the%20PCT%20changed%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20out%20the%20PCT%20alone%20and%20eventually%20joined%20up%20with%20a%20group%20I%20met%20on%20the%20trail%20before%20taking%20on%20a%20risky%20section.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20we%20were%20trying%20to%20walk%20around%20the%20snow%20by%20stepping%20on%20branches%20when%20one%20broke%20and%20impaled%20my%20calf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%20for%20me%2C%20one%20of%20my%20hiking%20companions%20was%20a%20Swedish%20Marine%2C%20so%20he%20helped%20provide%20medical%20treatment%2C%20hiked%20out%20with%20me%2C%20and%20then%20hiked%20back%20in.%20At%20the%20urgent%20care%20center%2C%20they%20gave%20me%20six%20stitches.%20That's%20how%20I%20ended%20up%20getting%20my%20trail%20name%3A%20Stitches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20to%20get%20off%20the%20trail%20for%20eight%20days%2C%20but%20the%20doctor%20said%20I%20could%20continue%20hiking%20with%20stitches%20and%20that%20he'd%20give%20me%20a%20suture%20removal%20kit%20to%20cut%20them%20out%20myself.%20So%20at%20one%20point%20when%20I%20was%20back%20with%20the%20group%2C%20the%20doctor%20ended%20up%20FaceTiming%20me%20and%20we%20just%20cut%20them%20out%20on%20the%20side%20of%20this%20mountain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trail%20is%20kind%20of%20like%20a%20wash%20cycle.%20It%20just%20keeps%20turning%20you%20and%20turning%20you%2C%20and%20every%20day%20you're%20struggling%20and%20it's%20aggravating.%20And%20then%20in%20the%20end%2C%20you're%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20I%20am%20different.%26quot%3B%20You%20come%20out%20more%20pure%20and%20more%20raw%20than%20you%20were%20before%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20you're%20less%20clean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20just%20opens%20your%20mind%20and%20opens%20your%20eyes%20to%20different%20ways%20of%20being%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20reminds%20you%20that%20you%20don't%20really%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20things%20that%20you%20have%20in%20your%20life%20to%20be%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20went%20back%20to%20work%2C%20I%20lost%20this%20identity%20of%20feeling%20so%20powerful%20and%20strong.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20lost%20a%20lot%20of%20direction.%20On%20the%20trail%2C%20you%20have%20such%20a%20clear%20north%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jessica%20Guo%20stands%20looking%20at%20mountains.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6802a745a466d2b74ab39ec7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJessica%20Guo%20plans%20to%20hike%203%2C700%20miles%20over%20150%20days%20this%20summer%20along%20the%20Continental%20Divide.%3Cp%3EJessica%20Guo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22784487c6-3a11-46f2-b976-f4ab0e04e920%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20realized%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20off%20the%20corporate%20ladder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20on%20a%20very%20defined%20career%20track.%20In%20consulting%2C%20you%20make%20associate%2C%20then%20senior%20associate%2C%20then%20manager%2C%20then%20senior%20manager%2C%20then%20director%2C%20and%20then%20partner.%20I%20was%20a%20manager%20and%20I%20am%20stepping%20off%20of%20that%20track%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20year%20after%20the%20PCT%20I%20realized%20I%20was%20at%20a%20point%20where%20you%20either%20commit%20to%20this%20track%20and%20you%20talk%20about%20becoming%20a%20partner%20at%20this%20firm%2C%20or%20you%20go%20and%20do%20something%20completely%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20at%20a%20crossroads%20and%20having%20a%20lot%20of%20conversations%20with%20people.%20Do%20I%20want%20to%20make%20this%20track%20my%20life%3F%20Do%20I%20want%20this%20life%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20the%20answer%20to%20that%20was%20probably%20not.%20%3Cspan%3EI%20felt%20like%20the%20things%20that%20I%20did%20on%20the%20trail%20were%20so%20much%20more%20life-giving%20to%20me%20than%20the%20lifestyle%20I%20had%20when%20I%20was%20working.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20lucky%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20I'm%20not%20leaving%20my%20firm%20on%20a%20bad%20note.%20I%20have%20that%20safety%20net%20of%20feeling%20like%20I%20can%20always%20come%20back%20if%20I%20want%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20I%20want%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20marry%20those%20work%20skills%20from%20my%20job%20at%20PwC%20%E2%80%94%20like%20coaching%20and%20facilitation%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20outdoors.%20After%20my%20hike%2C%20I'd%20like%20to%20start%20my%20own%20facilitation%20practice%20where%20people%20can%20experience%20the%20outdoors%2C%20whether%20that's%20over%20a%20couple%20different%20sessions%2C%20a%20weekend%2C%20or%20a%20week%20or%20two%2C%20and%20get%20a%20similar%20experience%20that%20I%20got%20from%20thru-hiking%20without%20necessarily%20having%20to%20invest%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20very%20scary%20to%20quit%20my%20job%2C%20especially%20in%20this%20economy.%20But%20for%20me%2C%20it's%20just%20the%20right%20time.%20If%20I%20stayed%20at%20my%20firm%20for%20another%20year%2C%20I%20would%20just%20be%20wasting%20my%20time.%20I%20would%20be%20languishing.%20I%20would%20get%20resentful%20that%20I'm%20spending%20my%20time%20on%20this%20when%20I%20know%20what%20I%20want%20to%20be%20doing%20is%20something%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20a%20dream%20now%2C%20do%20it%20now.%20If%20you%20wait%2C%20then%20maybe%20it'll%20be%20less%20reachable%20or%20less%20accessible.%20Follow%20that%20instinct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20quitting%20your%20job%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Akvlamis%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ekvlamis%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpwc-consultant-quit-hiking-pct-corporate-ladder-career-change-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745146802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680195c7a466d2b74ab387b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpwc-consultant-quit-hiking-pct-corporate-ladder-career-change-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jessica%20Guo%20quit%20her%20consulting%20job%20at%20PwC%20after%20hiking%20the%20Pacific%20Crest%20Trail%20made%20her%20realize%20she%20didn't%20want%20to%20stay%20on%20the%20corporate%20track.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40businessinsider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A157%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpwc-consultant-quit-hiking-pct-corporate-ladder-career-change-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pope%20wishes%20worshippers%20Happy%20Easter%20after%20serious%20illness%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745145217000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F