ations%20at%2095%2C%20apologies.%20Sharma%20eats%20everything%20and%20enjoys%20a%20good%20burger%20as%20much%20as%20he%20does%20his%20%3Cem%3Eroti-sabji%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Indian%20flatbread%20and%20vegetables).%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20meals%20don%E2%80%99t%20include%20super-power%20rendering%20ingredients.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20Sharma%20focuses%20on%20the%20food%20he%20feeds%20his%20mind.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20to%20surround%20yourself%20with%20wise%20people%E2%80%99s%20work%2C%20not%20people%20the%20media%20shows%20as%20saints%2C%20but%20real%20wise%20people.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20interjects%20here%2C%20pointing%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F199661%2Fbengaluru-start-up-innovation-visually-challenged-technology-app-new%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20the%20smartphone%20has%20occupied%20our%20lives%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20activates%20our%20reward%20systems%2C%20creating%20a%20sort%20of%20ephemeral%20joy.%20So%2C%20does%20Sharma%20avoid%20the%20smartphone%20entirely%3F%20%E2%80%9CNo.%20I%20use%20it.%20But%20the%20minute%20I%20find%20myself%20spending%20too%20much%20time%20on%20it%2C%20I%20ask%20myself%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20would%20I%20be%20doing%20if%20I%20weren%E2%80%99t%20using%20my%20phone%3F%E2%80%99%20Then%20I%20go%20do%20that.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsenior-citizen-bankey-lal-sharma-3-1744822493.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Bankey%20Lal%20Sharma%20prides%20himself%20on%20his%20flexibility%2C%20suggesting%20that%20mental%20resilience%20is%20the%20key%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsenior-citizen-bankey-lal-sharma-3-1744822493.jpg%201200w%