rigin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FoGe7fJ31WtY%3Fsi%3DBSt-lXl_TiBY7W6N%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%E2%80%99s%20design%20mastery%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20come%20as%20a%20surprise.%20He%20is%20following%20in%20the%20footsteps%20of%20a%20fabled%20architectural%20legacy.%20His%20father%2C%20Iftikhar%20Kadri%20%E2%80%94%20now%2097%20%E2%80%94%20gave%20Mumbai%20its%20beloved%20Nehru%20Centre%2C%20a%20living%20memorial%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Iftikhar%20had%20mentioned%20in%20an%20interview%2C%20the%20design%20was%20born%20out%20of%20wanting%20it%20to%20reflect%20the%20former%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20ideals%2C%20with%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20cylindrical%20shape%20portraying%20a%20nation%20reaching%20up%20towards%20the%20sky%20and%20its%20cross%20latticework%20alluding%20to%20the%20whorls%20of%20the%20rose%20flower%20that%20Nehru%20always%20wore%20in%20his%20lapel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20his%20father%2C%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20genius%20lies%20in%20architecting%20places%20that%20are%20rich%20with%20possibilities.%20His%20architectural%20vocabulary%20is%20angled%20towards%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F386103%2Fsustainable-architecture-in-india-green-pavers-cseb-earth-blocks-orient-stranded-board%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esimplistic%20design%20that%20aces%20functionality%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20reasons%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20design%20needed%20to%20be%20simple%3B%20I%20wanted%20people%20to%20experience%20the%20forest%20and%20its%20views.%20I%20did%20not%20want%20the%20structure%20to%20be%20too%20intrusive%20within%20the%20forest.%E2%80%9D%20I%20agree%2C%20the%20walkway%20cuts%20through%20the%20forest%20with%20finesse%2C%20almost%20like%2